reviewText: Stalwart 20th Century Fox contract player Tyrone Power would later comment that his best performance, by all estimates, was in the film "Nightmare Alley", but these three films are also a complement to his talents, and, the best among these, in this reviewer/cinephile's opinion would be "The Razor's Edge". "The Black Swan" (AA: 1942 Best Cinematography), "The Rains Came" (AA: 1939 Best Special Effects).
